  "text": "We have presently an activity between physical incarnations called healing and review of the incarnation. Was anything of this nature occurring prior to the veil between the physical incarnations? I and well. The incoate structure of this process was always in place, but where there has been no harm, there need be no healing. This too may be seen to have been of concern to Logoi which were aware that without the need to understand understanding would forever be left undone. We ask your forgiveness for the use of this misnomer, but your language has a pulsity of sound vibration complexes for this general concept.",
